1 for the privilege of selling hemp-derived cannabinoid products in this state at the
2 rate of sixteen cents ($0.16) per milligram or milliliter, as labeled on the product,
3 of delta-9 tetrahydrocannabinol or delta-8 tetrahydrocannabinol or any other
4 form of tetrahydrocannabinol sold.
