13 Section 9. KRS 243.030 is amended to read as follows:
14 The following licenses that authorize traffic in distilled spirits and wine and in cannabis-
15 infused beverages may be issued by the distilled spirits administrator. Licenses that
16 authorize traffic in all alcoholic beverages may be issued by both the distilled spirits
17 administrator and malt beverages administrator. The licenses and their accompanying
